    "Artificial intelligence (AI) algorithms are now essential for controlling, tracking, and using agricultural inputs optimally.",
    "This chapter examines the impact of Industry 4.0 on modern agriculture and the innovations in IPM in information technologies.",
    "The development of Industry 4.0 has significantly impacted modern agriculture, necessitating new solutions for improved agricultural production.",
    "Agriculture faces challenges and uncertainties, necessitating new solutions for all aspects of production.",
    "Integrated Pest Management (IPM) is the most popular and sustainable approach to controlling pests, but requires extensive knowledge, expertise, and observation."
